thread.title: Emmerdale

author: Fiona Flynn
title: Emmerdale
text:
Hour-long episode
Vanessa’s postnatal depression comes to a head on tonight's Emmerdale as she struggles to cope with baby’s Johnny’s operation and ends up making a devastating admission to Rhona. Elsewhere, Cain is still annoyed with Moira for setting him up with Kyle yesterday as well as being angry at Kerry for spilling the beans to his son on who his dad is. Would he not just step up and be a father already?? Never fear though, Debbie is on the case.
